Package com.doodeec.utils.network.listener

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BaseRequestListener<ResponseType>
    Base generic Request listener called by BaseServerRequest
    GSONRequestListener<GSONType>  
    ResponseListener<ResponseType>
    Response listener Intended to be used in network service, when request listener is processed from raw data to typed data The difference with SimpleResponseListener is that this interface declares also Cancel and Progress event listeners
    SimpleResponseListener<ResponseType>
    Response listener Intended to be used in network service, when request listener is processed from raw data to typed data
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JSONRequestListener
    Server request listener Every listener is supposed to implement own BaseRequestListener.onError(com.doodeec.utils.network.RequestError) method Every listener should also implement (override) one of onSuccess methods JSONRequestListener.onSuccess(org.json.JSONObject) or JSONRequestListener.onSuccess(org.json.JSONArray)
